        "type": "subheading",
        "value": "Robot Operating System (ROS)"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "ROS is a flexible framework for writing robot software. It is a collection of tools, libraries, and conventions that aim to simplify the task of creating complex and robust robot behavior."
      },
